Sentence is withheld.   Defendant is placed on probation to DOC for six (6) years.   Conditions of probation are:
1) AODA assessment and follow through;
2) Submit to random drug screens and pay for same;
3) Full-time employment, if able, as determined by DOC; 
4) Assessment/treatment/counseling as deemed appropriate by the Department's assessment process;
5) Ten (10) months in the Manitowoc County Jail, under the Huber Law.   Five (5) months to be served up front to commence on 02-02-16 by 6:00 p.m.   Five (5) months, stayed to be imposed at the agent's discretion.   Court authorizes release for relative care if the Huber Officer agrees that is appropriate.  
6) Pay costs of action; 
7) Pay supervision fees in an amount to be determined by DOC.  
Minutes.
